# Loaded by `vite` (npm run dev). Used by all developers locally.
# Override machine-specific values in a gitignored `.env` or `.env.local`.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.ballistiq.xyz
# Local Adapty: leave unset or use http://localhost:3000 — dev server proxies `/admin/api/adapty` to Express (see vite.config.ts).
# Override only if YOUR Express dev port is not 3000: set EXPRESS_DEV_PORT in the shell when starting Vite.
